{"id":49901,"date":"2024-02-23T09:35:00","date_gmt":"2024-02-23T04:05:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=49901"},"modified":"2023-09-22T17:38:16","modified_gmt":"2023-09-22T12:08:16","slug":"bedroom-cabinet-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-cabinet-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"13 Cute Bedroom Cabinet Designs to Refresh Your Space"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>A bedroom is your personal sanctuary where you can create a tranquil environment. Explore bedroom cabinets that can add to the design aesthetic.\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If left unattended, a bedroom cabinet can easily disrupt the cohesiveness of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom&#8217;s design<\/a>. It would be a good practice to research the best bedroom cabinet designs to choose the correct one for your haven.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want everything to match? Or not? Each setting has its advantages:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>WHEN YOU MATCH EVERYTHING<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You give the bedroom a solid and uniform foundation.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You highlight the principles of repetition and flow.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>WHEN YOU MIX AND MATCH&nbsp;<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It allows you to include different textures and styles.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It provides the bedroom with an eclectic and interesting personality.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can follow some design principles &#8211;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Choose a theme that mixes stability\/consistency and difference\/flair.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Start with a few furniture pieces if you don&#8217;t have a great vision and need a jumping-off point.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Create a conversation between all the elements of the bedroom rather than making it a bland, flat display.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use a balance between small-scale and large-scale items, soft and rough textures AND warm and cool colour tones to create harmony.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smartly incorporate a variety of sizes and shapes of furniture when mixing and matching materials.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mix tone-on-tone when pairing a family of hues\/variations of the same colour. For this, consider the darkness and lightness of different colours.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with implementing the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/basics-of-interior-design\/\">design principles<\/a>, you also need to research the types of lighting that you can incorporate into the bedroom cabinet design to enhance the aesthetic beauty and the view of the items stored inside them. Here are some popular options:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Spotlight<\/strong> helps you see the &#8216;thing&#8217; in a particular spot, even if the lights are off.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Accent Lighting<\/strong> is similar to spotlights but has a more &#8216;aesthetic than functional&#8217; purpose.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Task Lighting<\/strong> helps you to get the &#8216;task&#8217; done of accessing the smaller and more needed cabinet items.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Ambient Lighting<\/strong> helps to create an ambience in the bedroom&#8217;s environment.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Examples &#8211; <\/strong>LED Ceiling Lights\/Bulbs | Suspended Lamps | Pendant Lights | Adjustable Bedside Table Lamp | LED Strip Lights | Recessed Lighting | Wall Sconces | Floodlights | Under-Cabinet Lighting | LED Downlights | Dimmer Lights | Under-Cabinet Puck Lights.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some of the most popular and somewhat cute bedroom cabinet designs to look out for. Dive right in and make the best picks for your home.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Cabinet Design for Corners<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This bedroom corner cabinet design is the ideal solution for storage maximisation while efficiently utilising the unused bedroom corner space. It is a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/space-saving-design\/\">space-saving solution <\/a>wherein you can display your favourite books and magazines. Prop a mirror over it, and it works as a useful dresser.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/22165636\/bedroom-corner-cabinet-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom corner cabinet designs for storage maximization\n\" class=\"wp-image-49908\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/22165636\/bedroom-corner-cabinet-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/22165636\/bedroom-corner-cabinet-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/22165636\/bedroom-corner-cabinet-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/22165636\/bedroom-corner-cabinet-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bedroom corner cabinet substituting as a dresser  <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Storage Cabinets With Panels for Bedside<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The white side cabinet panels frame the super comfy lift-up bed. They give a homely vibe to the space and are customised with open shelves and drawers to store your souvenirs in an organised fashion. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/laminate-wood-flooring-designs\/\">wooden flooring<\/a> also complements the cabinet panels. Bedroom storage cabinets are the staple of any bedroom worth its salt.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/w