ook and Feel | Moisture-Resistant | Cost-Effective<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wood Plastic Composites &#8211; Pre-laminated sheets | Less Maintenance | Water-Resistant | Recyclable<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are the best colours for modern bedroom cabinets as per vastu?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Neutrals &amp; Whites &#8211; Makes the bedroom look spacious | Brings cosiness<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Light Wood Finish &#8211; Adds dimension and depth | gives a sleek look | Blends well with existing decor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Baby Yellow &amp; Green &#8211; Brings brightness and positivity into the space | Gives a vibrant &amp; airy touch<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A bedroom is your personal sanctuary where you can create a tranquil environment. Explore bedroom cabinets that can add to the design aesthetic.\u00a0 If left unattended, a bedroom cabinet can easily disrupt the cohesiveness of the bedroom&#8217;s design. It would be a good practice to research the best bedroom cabinet designs to choose the correct&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":49921,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":"","_wp_rev_ctl_limit":""},"categories":[11],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-49901","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-bedroom-interiors"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>13 Cute Bedroom Cabinet Designs For Storage | DesignCafe<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"A bedroom cabinet design is a thoughtfully created furniture piece that helps you adequately meet your storage needs. Click here to see our pretty designs.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-vide